{"tid":1743520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"區選唔投票個班 你有咩本錢去拒絕制度","createTime":"2019-11-21T08:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T09:09:11.000Z","uid":212260,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5eda843e94a302e2438af7af05b233f8cc8813fc","tid":1743520,"uid":212260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"起義又唔敢<br />\n罷工又唔肯<br />\n仲打曬飛機射落海都唔益假制度<br />\n同垃圾會投棄權票一樣<br />\n不如認左佢自己甘心做一隻大灣豬<br />\n再講多次<br />\n星期日共匪依然過半<br />\n我宣佈運動結束<br />\n香港冇得救"},{"pid":"81bc07d01a6b846741380cdc563777ab803874e0","tid":1743520,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U84oZn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU84oZn6.jpg&h=065a56a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMbyB1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMbyB1k.jpg&h=604a5751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期五夜晚，各區商場和理非唱歌，區選前最大型和理非行動，想問下你會唔會參與？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6025d732151e9f2e42c66b1564dedfb88163c336","tid":1743520,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:43:51.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=ed7fd954\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=9576f223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=8ab856cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameKCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=897d73c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"7cbdb5ed5a0ab18501111edbf7d3b907c56ee726","tid":1743520,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eda843e94a302e2438af7af05b233f8cc8813fc","tid":1743520,"uid":212260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"起義又唔敢<br />\n罷工又唔肯<br />\n仲打曬飛機射落海都唔益假制度<br />\n同垃圾會投棄權票一樣<br />\n不如認左佢自己甘心做一隻大灣豬<br />\n再講多次<br />\n星期日共匪依然過半<br />\n我宣佈運動結束<br />\n香港冇得救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"麻煩巴打幫手推推，而加成街對家文宣，自己友街站都少，勇武都幫手快閃貼文宣更加好，因為街坊貼而加都有危險。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民文宣鍵盤戰，不分和勇</span></strong></span><br />\n選舉文宣！文宣！文宣呀！唔夠對家多呀！的牆無曬喇！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743216</a>"},{"pid":"c7c88b35946598d87eb2dd99166d3bab84910832","tid":1743520,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:44:37.000Z","msg":"悔氣撚，拉"},{"pid":"e116de1a9502b472999edd71e6496112f651597d","tid":1743520,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb09389f510024525d6c387d421b6d20b18629d0","tid":1743520,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"一句講晒，嗰日去唔去投票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743477</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"83225a6efc83d1b339626734356f0f87fb320c7a","tid":1743520,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"【贏盡區選大行動】11月23,24 齊幫手 助區選<br />\n<br />\n保皇黨在每個投票站，設幾十個街角站，每個街站有二三十人助選，一眼睇就認出係大陸人。<br />\n<br />\n民主手足缺資源，欠缺助選員，如果大家只去投票，不去助選，輸咗議席只能後悔。<br />\n<br />\n建議：<br />\n1 22號去聯絡自己區要支持的候選人，約好23號24號助選時間及位置。<br />\n2 每個街站分配三四十人，人多再分配時間輪班。<br />\n3 有人行過，講明<span style=\"color: red;\">「今天香港亂局，完全因為保皇黨有議席，所以政府極惡横行無忌，令到百萬市民憤怒，出來反對暴政。唔想香港亂，踢走保皇黨，一定要投票(＃)號！」</span><br />\n4 【重要】保票站不衝突！有人挑釁，不回應，冷處理。離遠十步影低佢，日後放上網相討要唔要撕鳥。<br />\n<br />\n如果有多過一個似民主手足後選人，會有好大風險。<br />\n查看他 facebook/IG，五六月時有無日日發過多文，剷過政府。如果無就命令佢宣報退選，否則撕鳥。<br />\n如果兩個都有，要找佢地兩個傾掂，傾唔掂，叫佢哋曬馬(或facebook like人數)，邊位多人就出線，少人就退選。<br />\n大局最重要，一定<span style=\"color: red;\">只可一位出選</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n【贏盡區選大行動】11月23,24 齊幫手 助區選！只可一位出選<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743545</a>"}]}